OL,3,CFire service rescues people from
OL,4,Csuspected Coleraine arson
OL,6,FPolice are investigating a suspected
OL,7,Farson attack at a block of flats in
OL,8,FSociety Street, Coleraine, in the
OL,9,Fearly hours of Wednesday.
OL,11,FThe fire, which was reported to police
OL,12,Fshortly before 1am, is believed to
OL,13,Fhave been started in a communal area
OL,14,Finside the flats.
OL,16,FFire Service personnel attended and
OL,17,Fremoved a number of trapped
OL,18,Findividuals from the building before
OL,19,Fextinguishing the fire.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/3
