OL,3,CFire service rescues people from
OL,4,Csuspected Coleraine arson
OL,6,FAll other occupants were evacuated
OL,7,Ffrom their flats until it was deemed
OL,8,Fsafe to return and there were no
OL,9,Freports of any injuries.
OL,11,FThe PSNI are asking anyone who noticed
OL,12,Fany suspicious activity or who may
OL,13,Fhave captured dash-cam or CCTV footage
OL,14,Ffrom the area which could help with
OL,15,Ftheir investigation, to call them at
OL,16,FColeraine on the non-emergency number
OL,17,F101.
OL,19,FSign up for our free weekly newsletter
OL,20,Fhere.
